org.epochx.tools.grammar
Class TerminalSymbol

java.lang.Object
  org.epochx.tools.grammar.TerminalSymbol
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, Symbol
public class TerminalSymbol
extends java.lang.Object
implements Symbol

A terminal node of a parse tree, that was constructed to represent a specific instantiation of a GrammarLiteral of a grammar.

See Also:
NonTerminalSymbol, GrammarLiteral

equals

public boolean equals(java.lang.Object obj)
Tests the given Object for equality with this terminal symbol. The objects are considered to be equal if the argument is an instance of TerminalSymbol and the underlying grammar literals have matching literal values according to the String equals method.

Overrides:

Parameters:

Returns:
